author: Christina Zhao
title: Mexicans Will Block Southern Border Crossing Again Over Concerns Untested Americans Will Spread Coronavirus
description: Mexican protesters held up signs urging Americans to "stay at home."
content:
Protesters in Mexico blocked a U.S. southern border point of crossing for hours on Wednesday over fears that untested Americans will enter and spread coronavirus, and they have vowed to stop traffic for a second day.
